header.gameNote: Progressive Insurance Horizon League Championship - Semifinal

article.description: — Daniel Oladapo registered 19 points as third-seeded Oakland got past fourth-seeded Northern Kentucky 69-58 in the semifinals of the Horizon League tournament on Monday night.
article.headline: Oladapo's 19 leads Oakland over N. Kentucky 69-58 in Horizon
article.linkText: Oladapo's 19 leads Oakland over N. Kentucky 69-58 in Horizon
article.story: INDIANAPOLIS -- — Daniel Oladapo registered 19 points as third-seeded Oakland got past fourth-seeded Northern Kentucky 69-58 in the semifinals of the Horizon League tournament on Monday night. The Golden Grizzlies will face top-seeded Cleveland State in Tuesday's championship game. Rashad Williams had 17 points for Oakland (12-17). Jalen Moore added 14 points. Trevon Faulkner had 26 points for the Norse (14-11). Bryson Langdon added 14 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ Elements of this story were generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
